                    <h3 class="mb-3">4. Cancellation and Refunds</h3>
                    <p>Cancellation policies vary by hotel. Please review the cancellation policy before making a booking. Refunds, if applicable, will be processed according to the hotel's cancellation policy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mb-4">
