                <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="mb-3">7. Changes to Terms</h3>
                    <p>BudgetStay reserves the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of our service constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.</p>
